  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the programme is to facilitate the anticipation of dementia both in elderly
      patients suffering from this disease and in their carers and to diminish care burden in order
      to improve quality of life and daily functioning.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
